</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C954F5AC949C3AADCF507A988686577F" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="4FB43378BFAA7A5091BEDF52EFA97430" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="105B6B808D5333796269D5E1C691FDC9" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
As here defined, the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="9C050BBD7F0B7352D32A81CD22804356" authority="Jeannel, 1962" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Nothonepha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nothonepha" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Nothonepha</taxonomicName>
includes all species of the 
<taxonomicName id="B131B2E602FEBF23E1F20C3C165325FB" authority="Jeannel, 1962" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Antiperyphanes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Antiperyphanes" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Antiperyphanes</taxonomicName>
Complex possessing mesepisternal pits. Seven described species belong to 
<taxonomicName id="C0990F43297899A6D9779A920BC928AB" authority="Jeannel, 1962" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Nothonepha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nothonepha" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Nothonepha</taxonomicName>
:
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B7565C5DC7454067FA1B6A66B638267A" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName id="E3C2DC7529FDCE465FFE0FC261BB7C80" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion lonae" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lonae">Bembidion lonae</taxonomicName>
Jensen-Haarup, 1910 (Fig. 5D)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0A04EAD5C34F2FFFDB4C12C6A3CDB451" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName id="FD5683F7703897CCAFB76992B263FC0A" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion pallideguttula" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pallideguttula">Bembidion pallideguttula</taxonomicName>
Jensen-Haarup, 1910
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="52FC607D412D5D1E702D8B89E66CF8ED" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName id="03F3FFFEE84475656BBC1AE82ED0C199" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion eburneonigrum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="eburneonigrum">Bembidion eburneonigrum</taxonomicName>
Germain, 1906 (Fig. 5E)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="124E40A63241F2EC60AE61B478E10CD1" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName id="874D60AC2FA636D06AD61EF3533AE1D7" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion engelhardti" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="engelhardti">Bembidion engelhardti</taxonomicName>
Jensen-Haarup, 1910
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5F228699F2ABC30062146146501A5759" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName id="37742D660733D9591E0A6BC9EC2E2DFC" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion engelhardti subsp. engelhardti" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="engelhardti" subSpecies="engelhardti">Bembidion engelhardti engelhardti</taxonomicName>
Jensen-Haarup, 1910 (Fig. 5G)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D587116F09B054D55404E250FECE536D" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName id="D9247B3301FC69CD041CB9F9F8B69B10" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion engelhardti subsp. rayoda" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="engelhardti" subSpecies="rayoda">Bembidion engelhardti rayoda</taxonomicName>
Toledano, 2008
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="313404F167273A4CAA87AB0C7626393E" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName id="27093813F1386B7CAA202130E985CE1C" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion tucumanum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tucumanum">Bembidion tucumanum</taxonomicName>
(Jeannel, 1962) (Fig. 5F)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="155D9F6D9DE22920A51CE6FA63690CFF" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName id="200C2B588D2E442BB8FF09C8BD1F4D6B" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion germainianum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="germainianum">Bembidion germainianum</taxonomicName>
Toledano, 2002 (Fig. 5C)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="817504929B175961D2BAB2F8AAA392A0" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
<taxonomicName id="429C2B03DB1E2D149004F36B7908D6BF" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion tetrapholeon" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tetrapholeon">Bembidion tetrapholeon</taxonomicName>
Maddison, sp. n. (Figs 5A, B)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="72F97D495ACBA8F062E1BE607E56A685" pageId="19" pageNumber="132">
Four of these species (
<taxonomicName id="34FA061DD02C28DEEC6490A67FE55A90" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion germainianum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="germainianum">Bembidion germainianum</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="343EAC90193C03F9C3A0811C941B7B45" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion tucumanum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tucumanum">Bembidion tucumanum</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="5A80A410B1497E961DCBB78844AE1C41" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion engelhardti" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="engelhardti">Bembidion engelhardti</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="D8373953814992680C9F86C4F6513C61" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion eburneonigrum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="eburneonigrum">Bembidion eburneonigrum</taxonomicName>
) were formerly placed in subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="D5EDD902B02039AA47E2A739DAD6775E" authority="Jeannel, 1962" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Antiperyphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Antiperyphus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Antiperyphus</taxonomicName>
. In addition, there are at least three undescribed species (including 
<taxonomicName id="63416D4857E02A6BB72B4EB7F2C895FD" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Bembidion</taxonomicName>
sp. nr. lonae, sequenced here). The species figured by 
<bibRefCitation id="78AD6F2C44FB2EE330DB2297E373C9D3" author="Toledano, L" journalOrPublisher="Memoirs on Biodiversity" pageId="27" pageNumber="140" pagination="81 - 130" title="Systematic notes on the Bembidiina of the northern Andes with particular reference to the fauna of Ecuador (Coleoptera, Carabidae)." volume="1" year="2008">Toledano (2008)</bibRefCitation>
as 
<taxonomicName id="20ED48C6246587E523404137A667A19D" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion germainianum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="germainianum">Bembidion germainianum</taxonomicName>
is an undescribed species related to 
<taxonomicName id="1F28E53BC5B1065E1CFBDFCB57680329" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion germainianum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="132" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="germainianum">Bembidion germainianum</taxonomicName>
. A revision of the subgenus is in preparation (
<normalizedToken id="C10CB2D884648A016C7243879A0B659F" originalValue="Roig-JuÃ±ent">Roig-Junent</normalizedToken>
and Maddison).
</paragraph>
